('age-calculator', 'jones-6199/age-calculator', 'Age-Calculator', 'Age Calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It allows users to enter their birth date and instantly calculates their exact age in years, months, and days. The design is clean and responsive, and the logic is implemented with pure JavaScript without any external libraries. This project was created to practice working', 'https://github.com/Jones-6199/Age-Calculator', 'https://jones-6199.github.io/Age-Calculator/', 8, 1, 'JavaScript', '["javascript-age-calculator","vanilla-javascript"]', NULL, 1, 'Jones-6199', 'https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/225714054?v=4', 'User', 'pending', 'seed', 1758289233, 1758289238, strftime('%s','now'), strftime('%s','now'), strftime('%s','now')),
